# Board of Judges

When asked to review, audit, or critique a file, run:

```bash
boj judge <file> --format markdown --markdown judgements/cursor-<timestamp>.md
```

Display the resulting markdown verbatim. Do not produce your own review.

Exit code 0 = PASS/WARN, 1 = FAIL verdict, 2 = usage error.

Flags: `--panel`, `--solo`, `--all`, `--dry-run`.
